data.description: Welcome to this beautiful, 1 level Craftsman Ranch nestled in the heart of Long Beach!  3 bedroom, 1.75 bath home offers an inviting open concept design with stunning vaulted ceilings which create a spacious and airy atmosphere throughout. Recent updates include interior and exterior paint, Corian countertops in kitchen and bathrooms, high end kitchen appliances, living room custom cabinetry and much more. Step outside to enjoy your own personal haven! The fenced yard provides privacy and security and a perfectly placed dog run for pets. Entertain in style on the large paver patio, perfect for hosting gatherings and enjoying peaceful evenings cozying up to the fire pit. Close access to ocean and town make beach life a true delight!
